*Prvo* je došao na događaj. (He came to the event first.)

On je *prvo* mislio da je to nemoguće. (He first thought that it was impossible.)

*Prvom* prilikom nam je pokazao svoje nove knjige. (He showed us his new books the first time.)

Ono što je *prvo* istraženo bilo je vrlo zanimljivo. (What was first researched was very interesting.)

*Prvo* se zahvaliti za vašu gostoprimljivost. (First of all, thank you for your hospitality.)